caption;Versi 2
no;1
p;Jesus is all the world to me,
p;My Life, my Joy, my All;
p;He is my Strength from day to day,
p;Without Him I would fall.
p;When I am sad, to Him I go,
p;No other one can cheer me so;
p;When I am sad, He makes me glad,
p;He’s my friend.
empty
no;2
p;Jesus is all the world to me,
p;My friend in trials sore;
p;I go to Him for blessings, and
p;He gives them o’er and o’er.
p;He sends the sunshine and the rain,
p;He sends the harvest’s golden grain;
p;sunshine and rain, harvest of grain,
p;He’s my friend.
empty
