p;Jesus is all the world to me,
p;and true to Him I’ll be;
p;O how could I this friend deny,
p;When He’s so true to me?
p;Following Him I know I’m right,
p;He watches o’er me day and night;
p;following Him by day and night,
p;He’s my friend.
